These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, september, march
1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | march | january | september | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, sprite
4 different pets are kept: dog, guinea-pig, mouse, bird
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
4. the person drinking milk is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda    | iced-tea | sprite    |
| Food       | bird | guinea-pig | mouse  | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, fish, ferret
1. the person drinking water is not the owner of the hamster##6
2. the owner of the rat is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
8. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | fish | ferret | rat | hamster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, tea, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the person drinking tea##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | tea | 7up | hot-chocolate     | mirinda |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

