.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
House: cape-cod, victorian, futuristic, wooden
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the wooden house is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the futuristic house is the futuristic house##1
6. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
8. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | victorian | futuristic    | cape-cod  | wooden   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

