.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla, fish, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, gospel, reggae
1. the fan gospel is on the left or right of the fan country##3
2. the fan gospel is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
3. the owner of the snake is the fan d&b##1
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
5. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan country##1
7. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | turtle | chinchilla     | fish | snake |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | country | reggae      | d&b         |

