.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, lawyer, teacher
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, dutch, egyptian, indonesian
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the dutch is not the teacher##6
3. the russian is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the indonesian is in an even position##4
5. the indonesian is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the indonesian is the lawyer##1
7. the bartender is not the indonesian##6
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bartender  | lawyer | teacher    | fisherman |
| Transport   | dutch | indonesian | egyptian | russian  |

