.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, april, october
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
3. the fan indie is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the fan pop and the person who's birthday is in april##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | april | march    | may | october |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

