.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, mirinda, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, trike
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person drinking milk is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the bus is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person drinking milk##6
6. the person drinking 7up is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | water  | mirinda | 7up | milk |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike     | trike     | bus    |

