.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros, bluemaster, tiparillo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cricket, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is not the montecristo-smoker##6
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the oliveros-smoker and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the oliveros-smoker is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | montecristo  | bluemaster | tiparillo | oliveros |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | cricket   | water-polo |

