4. the person driving the quad-bike is not the nurse##6
5. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
6. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | nurse | pilot | entrepreneur      | bartender   |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | roller   | skateboard | quad-bike |

 